Plot
An hour before the five best Dutch dance crews fly to a contest in New York, the subsidized trip
is cancelled. Five dancers from totally different crews don't want to give up their free plane
ticket and go anyway. In New York they realize what they've done. They have no money, no plan
and no crew. But... They came to dance so there is only one thing to do. Together they form a
new crew and do everything they can to enter the contest they came for. In the mean time
they have to survive two weeks in New York without any cash
